Definition: a member of any of several British or American groups consisting predominantly of young people who shave their heads
Example: some engage in white supremacist and anti-immigrant activities and this leads to the perception that all skinheads are racist and violent
Synonyms: skin, bully, noun, group, skinheads, m, a, member, of, any, several, British, or, American, groups, consisting, predominantly, young, people, who, shave, their, heads, some, engage, in, white, supremacist, and, anti-immigrant, activities, this, leads, to, the, perception, that, all, are, racist, violent
Category: noun.person
